---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';

const pageContent = {
  title: 'About LILIE',
};
---

<MainLayout content={pageContent}>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">About LILIE</h1>
      
      <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          LILIE was founded with a vision to create digital experiences that blend artistic expression with cutting-edge technology. 
          We believe in the power of design to transform how people interact with digital spaces, making them more intuitive, 
          beautiful, and meaningful.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Our Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          We take a holistic approach to design and development, considering every aspect of the user experience. 
          From the subtle animations that guide interaction to the core architecture that powers functionality, 
          we craft each element with precision and purpose.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Our Team</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          Our team consists of passionate designers, developers, and creative thinkers who are dedicated to pushing 
          the boundaries of what's possible in digital design. We combine diverse perspectives and specialized expertise 
          to create solutions that are both innovative and effective.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Our Services</h3>
          <ul class="text-white/80 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Web Design & Development</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Interactive Experiences</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Brand Identity</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>UI/UX Design</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Digital Strategy</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Our Values</h3>
          <ul class="text-white/80 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Innovation in every project</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Attention to detail</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>User-centered design</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Sustainable development</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-white/50 mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Continuous learning</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
